### 上传学生头像
POST http://localhost:8080/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0ZXN0MDIiLCJ1c2VySWQiOjUsInJvbGUiOiJVU0VSIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgwOTIwMjE3LCJleHAiOjE3ODEwMDY2MTd9.2qnYjse5gdAxGCjMsepUkzgLWnwis5fm3ptQJAfwmjY
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< D:/New_java/student-system/student-api/test-avatar.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### 不带 token 上传头像，预期返回 401
POST http://localhost:8080/upload/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< D:/New_java/student-system/student-api/test-avatar.png
--WebAppBoundary--
